## STRATEGY

**What it is:** Tower defense, base-building, RTS-lite, deck-builder. *All Star Tower Defense*, *World // Zero*-adjacent strategy hybrids.

**Audience:** Older (15–30), broader globally, deeply committed when they bite.

**Session shape:** 20–45 min sessions, often co-op.

**Monetization fit:** Strong. New characters/towers, cosmetic skins, season passes, exclusive units. Strategy players will pay for breadth of options.

**Build difficulty:** **4/5.** AI/pathfinding, balance, content (units/maps), networking for co-op. Doable solo with patience.

**Saturation:** **2/5.** Roblox flagged this as **underrepresented**. Tower defense has incumbents but the broader strategy lane is open.

**Realistic earnings ceiling for a solo dev:** $1,000–$15,000/month. Tower defenses with anime/IP themes can push higher.

**Verdict:** **Underrated lane.** If you have strategy-game taste and are willing to invest in balance/content, this is a strong solo opportunity in 2026.

